OL,4,G2305FGreen Wing
OL,5,     GThe end is nigh. Caroline's now
OL,6,     Gengaged to Guy, while Mac has
OL,7,     Gvery little time to live. Statham
OL,8,     Gand Joanna are on the run,
OL,9,     Gjumping relentlessly out of
OL,10,     Gfrying pans and into fires.
OL,11,G0100FTattoo Fixers
OL,12,     GLou helps out tomboy Lucy, who
OL,13,     Ghas a vulgar phrase tattooed on
OL,14,     Gher leg, and Sketch gets a shock
OL,15,     Gwhen skater boy Matt shows him a
OL,16,     Gtattoo in an unsightly place.
OL,17,G0200FTaskmaster
OL,18,     GTensions bubble to the surface
OL,19,     Gduring an apparently simple team
OL,20,     Gtask. Plus: what constitutes a
OL,21,     Gloo roll? And how do you
OL,22,     Gentertain a toddler?
